#!/usr/bin/env bash [[ -f "${TM_SUPPORT_PATH}/lib/bash_init.sh" ]] && . "${TM_SUPPORT_PATH}/lib/bash_init.sh"
PROJECT=$(/System/Library/Frameworks/Ruby.framework/Versions/1.8/usr/bin/ruby -- "${TM_BUNDLE_SUPPORT}/bin/find_xcode_project.rb") if [[ -f "${PROJECT}/project.pbxproj" ]]; then "${TM_BUNDLE_SUPPORT}/bin/run_xcode_target.rb" -project_dir="$PROJECT" else echo "Didn't find an Xcode project file." echo "You may want to set TM_XCODE_PROJECT." fi
